net.sourceforge.seqware.pipeline.module
Interface RedirectAware

public interface RedirectAware

This module, in conjunction with the Tag and Run annotation are used to replace the old Module with the Runner code. The Methods used in ModuleInterface will be replaced by the Run annotation. The stdout/stderr will be replaced with this interface. Any metadata, such as, the algorithm will be replaced with the Tag annotation. Created by IntelliJ IDEA.
